Package: crash-crafts-game-sync
Version: @VERSION@
Section: games
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: CrashMediaIT <support@crashmediait.com>
Depends: ca-certificates, libc6
Description: Desktop companion for Crash Crafts Game Sync
 Crash Crafts Game Sync is a desktop companion daemon for the Docker-hosted
 sync server. It configures local emulator paths, runs background save sync,
 and generates Steam ROM Manager presets while server administration remains
 in the Docker Web UI.
